high_descs: Turn right and begin across the room, then turn left and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the metal fork off of the white table.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink and look up.
Open the cabinet door above the sink and place the metal fork inside the wooden cup.
Pick up the wooden cup with the fork inside of it and close the cupboard door.
Turn around and walk over to the white table on your right.
Place the wooden cup with the fork in it on the middle of the front edge of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a wooden cup with a fork in it on a white table.

high_descs: Turn to your right then turn to your left walk towards the table
Pick up the fork beside the cabbage on the table
Turn around to your left then head to the sink
Open the cabinet on above the sink
Get the glass on the cabinet above the sink and put the fork on the glass then close the cabinet
Bring down the glass turn to your left and head towards the table
Place the glass in front of the black container on the table
anns.task_desc: Put glass with fork on the table

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room to the left towards the white table.
Pick up the silver fork in front of the loaf of bread on top of the table.
Turn around, hang a left at the white table to reach the sink.
Open the cabinet above the metal bar on the wall and place the fork inside the goblet glass on the lower shelf.
Pick up the glass with the fork inside and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the white table on your right.
Place the glass with the fork inside in front of the black mug on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass with a fork on the table.

high_descs: Take a step to the right, and move forward to face the white table.
Pick up the fork from the center of the table.
Carry the fork and turn left to locate the sink.
Open the cabinet above, and and place the fork inside.
Pull out a cup with the fork in it from the cabinet.
Carry the cup and turn to the left and face to the white table on the left.
Place the cup and fork on the front center of the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a fork and cup to a white table.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the metal fork off of the table.
Turn around and walk towards the table, then hang a right and walk up to the sink and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the cabinet door in front of you and place the metal fork inside the cup that is inside.
Take the cup with the fork in it out of the cabinet and close the cabinet door.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the white table against the wall.
Place the cup with the fork in it in the middle of the front edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it on a white table.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, then turn left to go to the table.
Pick up the fork on the table, in front of the bread.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right to go to the sink.
In the cabinet above the sink, put the fork in the glass.
Pick up the glass with a fork in it, from the cabinet.
Turn around, go straight, then turn right to face the table next to the stove.
Place the glass on the table, in front of the mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a fork in it on the table.
